# Binary file types — prevent Git's autocrlf=true (Windows default) from
# converting LF→CRLF inside binary file streams.
#
# Triggered by WP-OneNote-Export-01 CI failure 2026-05-28: lopdf parses
# PDFs byte-exact; CRLF conversion corrupts the PDF trailer block on
# Windows clones, producing `Corrupted("Parse(InvalidTrailer)")` errors
# in the WP-EXPORT-01 pdf_extract test fixtures.
#
# Mac CI passes (no autocrlf); Windows CI fails the same tests on the
# same commit. Marking these extensions binary is the canonical fix.

# PDFs (added 2026-05-28 — was the immediate trigger)
*.pdf binary

# Image formats — Threshold ships icons; same risk pattern
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.ico binary
*.webp binary

# Bundle / executable formats — for shipped artifacts
*.dmg binary
*.exe binary
*.dll binary
*.msi binary
*.app binary
